const operation=(input,type,prevEva)=>{

    switch (type){

        case "geo": 
        case "square":
        case "pow":
        case "sqrt":
        case "pi":
        case "exp":
        case "factorial":
        case "percent":
        case "allClear":
        case "neg":
        case "delete":
        case "operator":
        case "result":
        default: break;     

    }


}

export default operation
